---
import { STUDIO_APPS } from "../lib/apps";
---

<footer class="footer">
	<div class="footer-main">
		<div class="footer-grid">
			<div class="footer-col footer-brand">
				<h4 class="footer-heading">Studio</h4>
				<p class="footer-desc">
					누구든 크리에이터가 될 수 있는 도구를 만듭니다.
				</p>
				<div class="footer-sns">
					<a href="https://instagram.com/modfolio.io" class="sns-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram">IG</a>
					<a href="https://linkedin.com/company/modfolio" class="sns-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn">LI</a>
					<a href="https://youtube.com/@modfolio" class="sns-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="YouTube">YT</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4 class="footer-heading">Products</h4>
				{STUDIO_APPS.map((app) => (
					<a href={`/apps/${app.id}`} class="footer-link" data-app={app.id}>
						{app.name}
					</a>
				))}
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4 class="footer-heading">Platform</h4>
				<a href="https://connect.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Connect</a>
				<a href="https://pay.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pay</a>
				<a href="https://docs.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docs</a>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4 class="footer-heading">Ecosystem</h4>
				<a href="https://works.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Works</a>
				<a href="https://ls.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LS</a>
				<a href="https://axiom.modfolio.io" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Axiom</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-legal">
		<p class="footer-biz">모드폴리오 · 대표 김동헌 · 사업자등록번호 104-95-65636 · 통신판매업 제2025-수원팔달-0953호 · 출판사 제2024-000037호 · 경기도 수원시 팔달구 효원로 278, 6층 602호 · contact@modfolio.io</p>
		<p class="footer-copy">© 2026 Modfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		background: var(--color-surface-raised);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
	}

	.footer-main {
		max-width: var(--layout-max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-16) var(--layout-padding-x) var(--space-12);
	}

	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: var(--space-8);
	}

	.footer-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-ui);
		font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--color-text-3);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.footer-brand {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-3);
	}

	.footer-desc {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: var(--font-size-small);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
		color: var(--color-text-2);
		max-width: 28ch;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.footer-sns {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-3);
		margin-top: var(--space-2);
	}

	.sns-link {
		font-family: var(--font-ui);
		font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
		color: var(--color-text-3);
		text-decoration: none;
		width: var(--space-8);
		height: var(--space-8);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
		border-radius: var(--radius-full);
		transition:
			color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-smooth),
			border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-smooth);
	}

	.sns-link:hover {
		color: var(--color-text-1);
		border-color: var(--color-text-1);
	}

	.footer-col {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-2);
	}

	.footer-link {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: var(--font-size-small);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
		color: var(--color-text-2);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-smooth);
	}

	.footer-link:hover {
		color: var(--color-text-1);
	}

	/* Products 링크에 앱별 hover 색상 */
	.footer-link[data-app="munseo"]:hover {
		color: var(--color-app-munseo);
	}

	.footer-link[data-app="umbracast"]:hover {
		color: var(--color-app-umbracast);
	}

	.footer-link[data-app="sincheong"]:hover {
		color: var(--color-app-sincheong);
	}

	/* 법적 정보 바 */
	.footer-legal {
		max-width: var(--layout-max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-6) var(--layout-padding-x);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: var(--space-4);
	}

	.footer-biz {
		font-family: var(--font-ui);
		font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
		color: var(--color-text-3);
		line-height: 1.6;
		max-width: 70ch;
	}

	.footer-copy {
		font-family: var(--font-ui);
		font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
		color: var(--color-text-3);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}

		.footer-legal {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
